Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那又为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我觉得石动同学很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被她给看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她给看透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看透了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡的饵食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌  朋与你真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也去「小爱」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  借我下英语字典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就放在橱柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就借走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个例题是积分基础中的基础
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家理解到很容易就能解开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘吗  给你那红果的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红果的数量表达了爱你的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己被她接二连三地诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒的源头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不错嘛  放学后的约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去抱怨几句而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心不要被她吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是石动乃绘？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑摩托车来接她？  好低级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真一郎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说过会儿就来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送去文化馆的慰问品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像非常好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快喂我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要唉声叹气的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在尝味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是喜欢吃掉了的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是小爱的料理  就算掉在地上我也会吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样很快会吃坏肚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃小爱的料理而死是正合我意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘有男朋友？  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她为什么要调戏你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是想要我代替雷轰丸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轰丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后庭的一只鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只鸡死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成那些红果是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只鸡的饵食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被圈养的鸡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有被圈养
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  我也得回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不早了啊  抄近路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了  前几天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打听了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是听说到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说想和乃绘做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实不是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她为什么会说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人这种动物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人这种动物一旦喜欢上别人  就会想更靠近对方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想更加更加靠近那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  当那个想法无法实现时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会想待在那个人附近的某个人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上像你这种人的女孩  真是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  比吕美喜欢上了某人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想要靠近那个人而待在乃绘身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个某人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃绘身边的男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  也没有别人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  腰再低一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸部运动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把嘴做横向运动  对健康有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸部运动…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸部运动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}被拜托了的  希望你能送去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你千万不要对对方失敬  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是急事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给船主大叔庆祝的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事明天去办不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了要在今天送去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个出门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送东西去大叔那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明用不着连阿真也一块儿去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话  让真一郎去不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让阿真去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让比吕美去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比吕美已经是我们家的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真一郎一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没必要跟我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路暗下来后很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且酒瓶也很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我受了你家的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这条路我们以前走过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的时候  和你走散了  哭得哇哇的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  关于昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说被看透了…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  其实我很害怕走这条路的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我  真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都封印在心里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当决定在这个家生活的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说不记得了  真受打击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  即便只是在一起走走也是进步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能抓紧我  于是伸出了手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那时  天空慢慢飘起了雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色  鲜红的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经这么晚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我今天要去准备男篮的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有时间的话会去加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去睡一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤川的男篮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也没别的事  去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  仲上君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是仲上君的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西一直连过去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那～家～伙～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  她在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了我不需要红果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是你说了算的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  我不知道你怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还是不要和我扯上关系比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有男朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你别再缠着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我下不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己爬上去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就自己下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂就在真一郎的脑子里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的背后也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么那边？  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边是哪里你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你  你的脚真疼假疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}那边  那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个4号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是乃绘的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误以为她老哥是男朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首先你就该确认一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙有没有男朋友  跟我又没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却松了口气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你有汤浅比吕美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是找个理由比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背石动乃绘的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才被她看得一清二楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见那个肯定会误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得找理由不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  麻烦你把球扔过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的你看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个傻瓜在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我无关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这样下去真的不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  比吕美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你喜欢仲上君不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石动乃绘的脚受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那家伙之间没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她突然就从树上跳了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  这不搞得好像真发生过什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放弃  我放弃  我放弃  我放弃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我不会对朋与你说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的是萤川的4号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不要再提真一郎君的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来…你是这么健谈的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  难不成你在躲着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乃绘交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 眼睛眨一眨
